t and determine OASIS \ncoding was gathered by the assessing clinician and documentation of the specific information/responses \nwas completed. \n\n\u2022  For row d, BOTH interventions (monitor and mitigate pain) must be both on the physician-ordered Plan of \n\nCare AND implemented for \u201cYes\u201d to be selected. \n\nCoding Instructions", "type": "Document"}}